Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really... What am I\Ngoing to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna step out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-chan, did you have another\Nfight with your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no fight. This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he apologizes, we're done for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna step out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't I be\Nable to play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's turn Kousei into a pianist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a genius!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm heading out now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going\Nto play? Without a violi-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not changing the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not music or anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just how great a musician Kaori Miyazono is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a supreme directive from the shrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These galas are all about standing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is a violin concert, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that accompanist\Ngoing to play on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is all your fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you put me\Nback on the stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always... you always move me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to prove it.\NThat I'm incredible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Kaori Miyazono, who's named\Nme to be her accompanist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is even more incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, unprecedented! Arima again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the accompaniment. This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kreisler... Love's Sorrow...\NRachmaninoff's Piano Arrangement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The song that Saki loved...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've been facing it\Nalone all this time. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the Love's Sorrow\Nthat you've always known?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just watch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just watch... Just watch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm incredible... Kaori Miyazono is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...even more incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.50,SSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbelievable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So powerful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a disappointment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's only venting his anger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's confusing crudeness with ferocity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This grates on my ears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I pounding the keys that hard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My whole body is taut...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This won't do at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This piece isn't... This isn't\Nhow you play it, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The song that I always listened to was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This song was my lullaby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I can't hear the notes as usual,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear the sound inside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it means that you're not bound by sounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wasn't there ever a moment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when you sensed the notes suffused\Nwith your desires and emotions?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Losing the ability to hear the notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure that that's... a gift.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play it more gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're caressing a baby's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play it like you're embracing him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom... This song... If it were her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would she have played it like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His playing style just changed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's doing it again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound is changing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Saki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saki is there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even for you, that's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hitting him hard enough to\Ndraw blood - that's way too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei was doing his best\Njust to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! Of course I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do know that... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me... Please help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help me... The notes...\NThe piano... My hearing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear the notes!\NSomebody... Please help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who drove\Nyou into this corner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all because I told her\Nto turn you into a pianist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If music only brings\NKousei pain and suffering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I have no business\Nbeing by his side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.25,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima\NSumitani Junior Highschool
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei has returned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What made you turn to the piano?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see that sight again\Nwith my own eyes one more time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what made me think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd like become\Na really weird pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After losing Saki, Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...met someone who\Nmeans the world to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Kousei believes in\Nthat, then as a pianist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how can I not believe\Nin the power of music?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saki. Be sure to watch this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That son of ours{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is about to bid you a last farewell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't help thinking\Nabout her, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This song has my mother's scent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you going to play it for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it reach her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope it reaches her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I'm gone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to become of Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will be able to earn a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can he make music his livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I can do right now is make him\Nplay accurately, faithful to the score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as he has the skills, he just\Nmight be able to support himself someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can leave that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will he brush his teeth every morning?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He falls asleep anywhere,\Nso what if he catches a cold?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He isn't good at sports,\Nso what if he gets seriously injured?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've stayed with him longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will my treasure... ever find happiness?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew all along. The ghost of my\Nmother was a shadow of my own creation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An excuse for me to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My own weakness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom isn't there anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom... is inside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, that's right. The piano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is meant to be played like\Nyou're embracing it, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hey... Mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's both Love's Joy\Nand Love's Sorrow, so why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...do you always play Love's Sorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I play it so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll get used to sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all connected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like the notes\Nare intermittently connected...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's shared by us all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through music...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the people you know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the people you don't know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with all the people in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You come, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like with her, I'm\Nconnected to Mom, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm moving forward\Nbecause I believe that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My knees are shaking...\NGuess I'm exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at you, hot stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If my husband hears that his daughter\Nthrew herself into a man's arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So did you get to see Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way I touch the keys, the way I move my\Nfingers, my habit of squeezing the pedals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my tastes, the order that I eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's in every little\Ngesture of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're... Mom and I are... Connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko-san... Do you\Nthink it reached my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way I played my very best...\NDo you think it reached Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. You two\Nare connected, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it reached her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of music, I was given\Nthe chance to meet others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was moved by those encounters.\NThere are people that I got to meet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got to discover emotion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These are all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...memories that my mother, who taught\Nme how to play the piano, left me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom, I'm happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you. Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was so exquisite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to just go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the next performance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never thought I'd be\Nso scared to go onstage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miike-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now this is a tough act to follow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to run away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would I have played my\Nheart out like he did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would I have played with\Nas much sincerity as he did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see if I can sacrifice\Nbody and soul like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see if I\Ncan give it all I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just watch me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, all I want to do\Nis hear my mom's voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is his playing softer\Nthan usual? I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So your heart's been pierced, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you're both going to raise the bar, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't violin music lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I'm a musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To obliterate a powerful enemy...\NNow that's the ultimate pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A bona fide extreme sadist?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? This is so weird...\NI can't find the words to say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Freaky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it okay for you to just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not? I was just a throw-in\Nfor the throw-in. And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find that throw-in who\Nblew me off, and rip her a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's mad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, ready to head home?\NI'm exhausted from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your mom could go for some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nothing to say to me\Nafter all my hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um... You look all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? I was\Nhoping you'd praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck? So weird...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't hold them in,\NI might shed tears. Tears?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears of relief because I was\Nable to talk to Kousei normally?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or because I was able\Nto talk to him normally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...tears of disappointment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.35,Maihou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were there at the concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you could've said something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're as spiteful as ever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ochiai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Arima-kun was being\Nmentored by you... That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, ever since Saki Arima passed\Naway, you never went near that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy has changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's become quite an intriguing musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Instilling something into his music,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,leaving something in those who hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That kid has taken his first\Nsteps forward as an artist. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The loss of Saki Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was tragic for Kousei, and for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but was it really necessary for\NKousei Arima, the musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's an ever-present sorrow\Nhanging over Arima-kun's music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the death of his beloved mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}triggered something in him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then it's a demon's path\Nthat he must walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.34,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His growth is spurred by sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Kousei is to walk that path,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:20.10,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love's Sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he might have to lose someone to move forward.
